parameters.description:
Specify the other details of user which you want to create in JSON format. e.g. {
                    "schemas": [
                      "urn:ietf:params:scim:schemas:extension:sap:2.0:User"
                    ],
                    "name": {
                      "formatted": "",
                      "middleName": "",
                      "honorificPrefix": "Mr.",
                      "honorificSuffix": ""
                    },
                    "title": "Developer",
                    "active": true,
                    "profileUrl": ""
                  } 
More details can be found here: https://api.sap.com/api/IdDS_SCIM/resource

