parameters.description:
Specify additional operations in JSON format to perform on user attributes. e.g. [
            {
              "op": "remove",
              "path": "emails[type eq \"work\" and value eq \"user@example.com\"]"
            },
            {
              "op": "add",
              "path": "nickName",
              "value": "user_nickname"
            }
          ]
